content.rendered:
Directed by Chandra Sekhar Yeleti.

Written by Ravichandra Teja Kandra. Padmavathi Malladi. Chandra Sekhar Yeleti.

Cast Mohanlal(Sairam). Gautami(Gayathri). Viswant Duddumpudi(Abhiram). Raina Rao(Mahitha). Avantika(Mahitha’s Friend (as Avantika Vandanapu)) . Anisha Ambrose(Aira). Darbha Appaji Ambarisha(Doctor).P. Balachandran.Bikshu. Brahmaji(Police Inspector). Chandramohan(Sadha Shivam Reddy).Chandrasekhar.Anitha Chowdary.Rudra Dev.Dhanraj.Harshavardhan. Vennela Kishore(Bhushan).Chaithanya Krishna.Joy Mathew.Baby Meghana.Melkote. Taraka Ratna Ramarao Nandamuri(Roadside Painter (as Taraka Ratna)).V.K. Naresh. Nassar(School Principal).Naveen Neni.Praveen.G. Maruti Rao.Paruchuri Venkateswara Rao. Sanjay Reddy(Heroine’s Father).Pammi Sai.Santhoshi Sammidi. Ayyappa P. Sharma(Dass).L.B. Sreeram. Urvashi(Gayathri’s Neighbour).Nedumudi Venu

Languages Telugu. Malayalam.

Producers Rajani Korrapati. Sai Korrapati.

Production Vaarahi Chalana Chitram.
